ve consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 9773, \"to\": 10405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9810, \"end\": 9817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.273100816416521e-31, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 10065, \"end\": 10070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"score\": 0.9999254998696819, \"rank\": 7.450568069210955e-05, \"text\": \"Kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\"}, {\"begin\": 10100, \"end\": 10103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.999999261080393, \"rank\": 4.6677584010169853e-07, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 10122, \"end\": 10132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999979844308049, \"rank\": 2.0155736812148003e-06, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 10175, \"end\": 10189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Kinsella\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alice Kinsella\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Kinsella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Kinsella\"}, {\"begin\": 10194, \"end\": 10212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia-Mae_Fenton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Georgia-Mae Fenton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia-Mae_Fenton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia-Mae_Fenton\"}, {\"begin\": 10279, \"end\": 10293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Stephens\", \"score\": 0.9999948522786944, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Stephens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Stephens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Stephens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 10406, \"to\": 10482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 10483, \"to\": 10515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Bev Priestman, the Canadian football coach at the centre of a spying scandal, has sensationally claimed that the men's side have a 'whole operation' on it.\", \"from\": 10516, \"to\": 10695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10559, \"end\": 10567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999996453289616, \"rank\": 3.5467091585398166e-07, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also made the astonishing allegation that 'all top 10 teams spy' in a bombshell email that emerged after her team were caught flying a drone over an opposition training session, according to theDaily Mail.\", \"from\": 10697, \"to\": 10906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after Canada's appeal against their six-point deduction and Priestman's year-long ban was dismissed by the Court of Arbitration for Sport.\", \"from\": 10908, \"to\": 11055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10923, \"end\": 10929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9921074068379324, \"rank\": 0.0054868811434239636, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the email, which was reportedly sent in March, Priestman said: \\\"I know there is a whole operation on the men's side with regards to it.\", \"from\": 11057, \"to\": 11195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On Tuesday, in a meeting when discussing, I asked to propose a alternative solution as for scouting it can be the difference between winning and losing and all top 10 teams do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 11197, \"to\": 11378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hello and welcome to Express Sport's rolling coverage of the latest news on day six of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 11382, \"to\": 11482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB will be hoping to increase their medal tally over the next few hours, with plenty of opportunities for gold, silver and bronze to be won.\", \"from\": 11484, \"to\": 11629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11484, \"end\": 11491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.273100816416521e-31, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will be bringing you the biggest stories from Paris throughout the day, so grab yourself a coffee and stay tuned...\", \"from\": 11631, \"to\": 11749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11680, \"end\": 11685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.022544835849442e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GBwill be hoping to add to their gold medal tally on day six of theOlympicswith a jam-packed schedule on the horizon.\", \"from\": 11753, \"to\": 11875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It could be a big day in the rowing, with Helen Glover competing in the women's four alongside Esme Booth, Samantha Redgrave and Rebecca Shorten.\", \"from\": 11876, \"to\": 12021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11918, \"end\": 11930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\", \"score\": 0.9968858553500259, \"rank\": 0.0031234382808579173, \"text\": \"Helen Glover\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helen_Glover_(rower)\"}, {\"begin\": 11983, \"end\": 11991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samantha_Mulder\", \"score\": 0.9687000268708231, \"rank\": 0.03231131646602612, \"text\": \"Samantha\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samantha_Mulder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samantha_Mulder\"}, {\"begin\": 12005, \"end\": 12020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Shorten\", \"score\": 0.9999947512179875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebecca Shorten\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Shorten\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Shorten\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy MurrayandDan Evansare back on court at Roland Garros as they face the American pairing of Tommy Paul and Taylor Fritz in the men's tennis doubles.\", \"from\": 12023, \"to\": 12174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12098, \"end\": 12106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999996753104, \"rank\": 1.7921707513910945e-10, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 12118, \"end\": 12128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.313252888609354e-27, \"text\": \"Tommy Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http: